desc: Service split into Upper Valley service area which includes North Bend, Snoqualmie, Fall City, and Preston, and Lower Valley service area which includes Monroe, Duvall, and Carnation. The service typically connects with the fixed route service for travel between the Upper and Lower Valley but a one-seat ride is sometimes available.
